{"tid":2409741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一條人命十個月，漁護署農林助理員危駕引致他人死亡　判監10個月兼停牌","createTime":"2021-02-16T05:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:44:34.000Z","uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbc26cea67d001cc81b787d13286ef75206b21d","tid":2409741,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"一名女農林助理員，去年3月駕駛朋友的私家車，在屯門大興邨停車場駛出時，撞死一名男途人再撞到一架輕鐵列車，被告承認一項危險駕駛引致他人死亡罪，今日在區域法院被判監10個月，並須停牌5年及參加駕駛改進課程。 <br />\n<br />\n法官祁士偉在判刑時，報告顯示48歲的被告對死者家人感到極度愧疚，案發後有心理創傷。被告過去無犯案紀錄，意外發生後有真誠悔意，雖然被告駕駛態度危險，但法官認為危險程度屬最低一種，考慮到死者當時無利用行人天橋過路，及被告意外後有很大創傷，將原來的18個月的量刑起點調低3個月，再扣減認罪刑期，最終判監10個月。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379230&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=64336ea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379230</a>"},{"pid":"7819ab367636539db71d0172b7b47bf59fc33791","tid":2409741,"uid":140093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"死人10個月？"},{"pid":"7e9746577ead85b16cbbeba03b773642c370148f","tid":2409741,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"認為危險程度屬最低一種，考慮到死者當時無利用行人天橋過路，及被告意外後有很大創傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77ddc0e74ad3a8ed9ad18a37c66758a7e117f2b","tid":2409741,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"好記得呢單 十個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f387e96985fcfddbd6b5868f7fe564598e6947b9","tid":2409741,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"揸車撞死人不嬲好輕<br />\n半年以下都有"},{"pid":"b989ced3be9b2f28b6bc58fa67119d7ffe779f8d","tid":2409741,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48b5fcd4dce69dc2482b63c66a37a5eb7a82a0f","tid":2409741,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"Laser pointer都係十個月"},{"pid":"d197b87f7b58fc6cbee83058deaa510eac00fc0a","tid":2409741,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"香港法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ea6ac7ce62343f1210485012ab2238a705173a","tid":2409741,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f387e96985fcfddbd6b5868f7fe564598e6947b9","tid":2409741,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"揸車撞死人不嬲好輕<br />\n半年以下都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"試過緩刑,狗官仲幫講好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cc8b3d5614356d36de587d7f2f4bb90ec4b4b7","tid":2409741,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"因為係意外 + 無預謀 香港法律一定判好輕"},{"pid":"df332345f760e51889aee34c56ca72f553dce614","tid":2409741,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:42:22.000Z","msg":"又係女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420917663535549d8c7545cf817573c851b9227b","tid":2409741,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"屌，仲要區域法院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}